    "body": "## Purpose\r\n\r\nAs of now, when using the flag `--quantization fp8` some models like Qwen2.5-VL have some layers with incompatible shapes to use `torch.ops._C.cutlass_scaled_mm` (not divisible by 16) and the fallback is to use `triton_scaled_mm`. As a result the performance of FP8 is inferior compared to FP16.\r\n\r\n## Nsys traces\r\n**Triton**\r\n<img width=\"483\" height=\"561\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-05-06 at 15 38 20\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/766b472b-60d0-4d09-9c50-bf8e9d9b243c\" />\r\n\r\n**Cutlass**\r\n<img width=\"387\" height=\"552\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-05-06 at 15 40 23\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3ea5a138-c737-4ead-b6f2-f2a6d9f17817\" />\r\n\r\n## Test Plan\r\nModified `tests/kernels/quantization/test_cutlass_scaled_mm.py` to include non-compatible shapes\r\n\r\n## Benchmark\r\nlaunch engine\r\n```\r\nvllm serve Qwen/Qwen2.5-VL-7B-Instruct \\\r\n  --max-model-len 8192 \\\r\n  --no-enable-prefix-caching \\\r\n  --max-num-batched-tokens 2048 \\\r\n  --distributed-executor-backend uni \\\r\n  --max-num-seqs 64 \\\r\n--block-size 16 --quantization fp8\r\n```\r\n\r\nBenchmark\r\n```\r\nvllm bench serve \\\r\n  --base-url http://127.0.0.1:8000 \\\r\n  --endpoint /v1/chat/completions \\\r\n  --backend openai-chat \\\r\n  --dataset-name random-mm \\\r\n  --input-len 512 \\\r\n  --output-len 60 \\\r\n  --random-mm-base-items-per-request 1 \\\r\n  --random-mm-num-mm-items-range-ratio 0 \\\r\n  --random-mm-bucket-config \"{(512,512,1): 1.0}\" \\\r\n  --random-mm-limit-mm-per-prompt '{\"image\": 1}' \\\r\n  --num-prompts 1200 \\\r\n  --num-warmups 120 \\\r\n  --request-rate 36\r\n```\r\n**Currently with Triton**\r\n```\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nSuccessful requests:                     1200\r\nFailed requests:                         0\r\nRequest rate configured (RPS):           36.00\r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  237.25\r\nTotal input tokens:                      1028399\r\nTotal generated tokens:                  72000\r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              5.06\r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         303.48\r\nPeak output token throughput (tok/s):    2242.00\r\nPeak concurrent requests:                1096.00\r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          4638.16\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          102755.09\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        103007.08\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           201650.52\r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          194.97\r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        199.34\r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           210.89\r\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           191.72\r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         64.37\r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            529.83\r\n==================================================\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Proposed changed with Cutlass**\r\n```\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nSuccessful requests:                     1200\r\nFailed requests:                         0\r\nRequest rate configured (RPS):           36.00\r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  54.03\r\nTotal input tokens:                      1028399\r\nTotal generated tokens:                  72000\r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              22.21\r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         1332.49\r\nPeak output token throughput (tok/s):    2762.00\r\nPeak concurrent requests:                529.00\r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          20364.83\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          10076.78\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        9905.53\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           20078.51\r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          45.04\r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        46.30\r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           47.69\r\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           44.41\r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         40.87\r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            100.79\r\n==================================================\r\n```\r\n\r\nI found this old [PR](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/17558) that mentioned `Note that this could change behavior for CUDA since it will now run the triton kernel if the cutlass kernel isn't satisfied`.\r\nBefore there was an assert, but it was removed:\r\n```\r\nassert (b.shape[0] % 16 == 0 and b.shape[1] % 16 == 0)\r\n```\r\n\r\nPerhaps we can use the padding as a workaround.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Low latency benchmark\r\nCommand\r\n```\r\nvllm bench serve \\\r\n  --base-url http://127.0.0.1:8000/ \\\r\n  --endpoint /v1/chat/completions \\\r\n  --backend openai-chat \\\r\n  --dataset-name random-mm \\\r\n  --input-len 64 \\\r\n  --output-len 16 \\\r\n  --random-mm-base-items-per-request 1 \\\r\n  --random-mm-num-mm-items-range-ratio 0 \\\r\n  --random-mm-bucket-config \"{(512,512,1): 1.0}\" \\\r\n  --random-mm-limit-mm-per-prompt '{\"image\": 1}' \\\r\n  --num-prompts 200 \\\r\n  --num-warmups 40 \\\r\n  --request-rate 1\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Current status `main branch` commit `8189a15914ca48461acf106f126c58ef7e41c9ee `**\r\n\r\nNo quantization flag\r\n```\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nSuccessful requests:                     200\r\nFailed requests:                         0\r\nRequest rate configured (RPS):           1.00\r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  200.22\r\nTotal input tokens:                      81800\r\nTotal generated tokens:                  3200\r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              1.00\r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         15.98\r\nPeak output token throughput (tok/s):    68.00\r\nPeak concurrent requests:                5.00\r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          424.52\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          81.42\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        80.68\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           106.75\r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          10.74\r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        10.34\r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           13.10\r\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           10.40\r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         10.99\r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            35.47\r\n==================================================\r\n```\r\n\r\nQuantization flag\r\n```\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nSuccessful requests:                     200\r\nFailed requests:                         0\r\nRequest rate configured (RPS):           1.00\r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  200.30\r\nTotal input tokens:                      81800\r\nTotal generated tokens:                  3200\r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              1.00\r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         15.98\r\nPeak output token throughput (tok/s):    82.00\r\nPeak concurrent requests:                7.00\r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          424.36\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          240.69\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        200.87\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           540.53\r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          8.25\r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        6.62\r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           27.33\r\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           8.02\r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         6.98\r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            9.15\r\n==================================================\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Proposed changes**\r\nQuantization flag:\r\n```\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nSuccessful requests:                     200\r\nFailed requests:                         0\r\nRequest rate configured (RPS):           1.00\r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  200.17\r\nTotal input tokens:                      81800\r\nTotal generated tokens:                  3200\r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              1.00\r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         15.99\r\nPeak output token throughput (tok/s):    68.00\r\nPeak concurrent requests:                5.00\r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          424.64\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          74.72\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        73.82\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           103.17\r\n-----Time per Output Token (excl. 1st token)------\r\nMean TPOT (ms):                          6.52\r\nMedian TPOT (ms):                        6.32\r\nP99 TPOT (ms):                           8.51\r\n---------------Inter-token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           6.11\r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         6.32\r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            9.90\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n```\r\n",
